102
00:10:08.149 --> 00:10:09.442
<i>The server?</i>

103
00:10:09.526 --> 00:10:12.153
<i>It houses all</i>
<i>of Babylon's classified files.</i>

104
00:10:12.237 --> 00:10:14.823
<i>They've been around</i>
<i>since the military dictatorship.</i>

105
00:10:14.906 --> 00:10:17.242
<i>Babylon's carried out</i>
<i>all the intelligence operations.</i>

106
00:10:17.325 --> 00:10:19.119
<i>kidnappings. and assassinations</i>

107
00:10:19.202 --> 00:10:20.829
<i>on behalf of every changing regime.</i>

108
00:10:20.912 --> 00:10:23.790
Including selling North Korea weapons
behind our government's back.

109
00:10:24.749 --> 00:10:27.168
In the conflict zones
of Southeast and Central Asia.

110
00:10:27.252 --> 00:10:30.213
<i>they made arms deals</i>
<i>with both rebels and government forces.</i>

111
00:10:30.296 --> 00:10:32.924
